<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .order-details {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .order-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your purchase at EduVista! We are excited to confirm your order. Here are the details of your purchase:</p>

        <div class="order-details">
            <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= order._id %></p>
            <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= order.name %></p>
            <p><strong>Price:</strong> $<%= order.price %></p>
            <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></p>
        </div>

        <p>To view your course and start learning, please sign in to your account.</p>
        <a href="" class="btn">Sign In</a>

        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        EduVista</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

